  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>BayView Restaurant</strong> – is a lovely setting to enjoy breakfast and dinner, both are served buffet style. Breakfast can be taken from 7.30am to 10am, and dinner from 6.30pm to 9pm (selected meals are bookable and payable locally depending on board basis).</p>
<p><strong>Desarma Restaurant</strong> – a new addition to the hotel, this restaurant sits at the top of The Views Baia and offers delicious flavours mixed with traditional Madeiran ingredients (not included in the bed and breakfast, half-board and full-board basis).</p>
<p><strong>Pool Deck Bar</strong> – is situated right next to the outdoor pool - perfect for purchasing a cocktail and admiring those ocean views.</p>
<p><strong>Woogie Boogie cocktail Bar</strong> – open in the evenings, this elegant cocktail bar with floor to ceiling windows is a great spot for buying yourself a beverage.</p>
<p>Guests on half board or full board and staying on the 24th Dec 2024 and/or 31st Dec 2024 can enjoy a fantastic Christmas and/or New Years Eve Gala Dinner - these are included in the price of your holiday.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
