  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Views Baia hotel, is an adults-only escape with modern design and beautiful views.</p>
<h2>Cosmopolitan feel</h2>
<p>The hotel has a fantastic location. It’s set back from the sea but has an elevated position above Funchal Bay. You get to enjoy the natural amphitheatre of Funchal with mountains sweeping all around you and beautiful, distant views of the Atlantic Ocean ahead. You’re not too far from Funchal here so you can head into the centre and enjoy sightseeing, great food or wander the cobbled, historic streets.</p>
<h2>A pool with a view</h2>
<p>We love to hit the outdoor swimming pool on beautiful blue-sky days - the views are spectacular and it’s lovely to relax or take a dip in the pool. You’ll also find the Pool Deck Bar here where you can purchase a delicious beverage. As well as another bar, the hotel also has two restaurants (only one restaurant is included in the bed and breakfast, half-board and full-board basis).</p>]]></description>
